<HEADLINE>
UNDATED: the ninth. Athletics 2, Diamondbacks 1, 11 innings 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
	   In Oakland, California, Mike Blowers singled in the tying run in
the ninth inning and drove in the game-winner in the 11th as the
Athletics beat the Diamondbacks.
	   Both teams scored a run in the ninth on two-out RBI singles,
with Jay Bell opening the scoring for Arizona and Blowers
countering for Oakland.
	   Mike Mohler (1-2) got the victory with an inning of scoreless
relief, and Russ Springer (3-3) took the loss.
	    &UR; END
