<SLUG> BC-AP News Digest,0951 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
	   WORLD AT 1700 GMT:
	   NEW:
	   _GERMANY-BACK ON TRACK. Germans still confident in high-speed
trains.
