star. Arantxa Sanchez Vicario went to the Red Star stadium at
Saint-Ouen to see a friendly match between Brazil and Andorra.
Sanchez Vicario lives in the principality of Andorra.
	   Despite the loss of the Andorrans, Arantxa showed her sense of
fair play, and went to the locker rooms to say hello.
	   Ronaldo was so charmed, he gave her his soccer jersey. 	   
