<HEADLINE>
Tunisia beats Wales 4-0 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
	   TUNISIA, Tunisia (AP) _ Tunisia easily beat Wales 4-0 on
Saturday in a friendly match ahead of the World Cup.
	   Imed Ben Younes took advantage of a risky move by the Welsh
goalie, who briefly left the goal and allowed the Tunisian player
to score.
