<TEXT>
	   It was the second heartbreaking Belmont loss for trainer Bob
Baffert. His Silver Charm missed the Triple Crown last year when he
was beaten by Touch Gold by three-quarters of a length.
	   Silver Charm was ridden by Gary Stevens, who on Saturday was on
Victory Gallop.
