trounces Australia 7-0 in its last warmup match before the World
Cup.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-Croatia-Australia. Has moved.
	   SENLIS, France _ Roberto Baggio is a happy man these days.
Richer with a newly signed prestigious contract with Inter Milan,
the imaginative Italian soccer veteran is expected to start in
Italy's World Cup opener against Chile.
